OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMobile loophole for gaming 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdrivers is closed          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A loophole allowing drivers to escape  
OL,6, punishment for hand-held phone use if  
OL,7, they are taking a photo or playing a   
OL,8, game has closed in Great Britain.      
OL,10,FPeople can now be fined up to #1,000   
OL,11,Fand receive six points on their licence
OL,12,Ffor scrolling through playlists or     
OL,13,Ftaking pictures on a handheld device.  
OL,15,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said  
OL,16,Fthe government was taking a            
OL,17,F"zero-tolerance approach".             
OL,19,FDevices can still be used hands-free   
OL,20,Fwhile driving if secured in a cradle.  
